fields.name: Essential
fields.description: Essential cookies required for basic site functionality. These cannot be disabled.

fields.name: Media
fields.description: Cookies used for external media services, which may include tracking user behavior across websites. Required for YouTube video embedding.

fields.name: Analytics
fields.description: Cookies used to collect information about how visitors use our website, helping us improve performance and user experience. Includes New Relic monitoring.

fields.name: sessionid
fields.description: Session identifier cookie required for user authentication and maintaining session state.

fields.name: csrftoken
fields.description: CSRF protection token required for secure form submissions and preventing cross-site request forgery attacks.

fields.name: VISITOR_INFO1_LIVE
fields.description: YouTube cookie that tracks user behavior and preferences for embedded video content.

fields.name: YSC
fields.description: YouTube cookie that registers a unique ID to keep statistics of what videos from YouTube the user has seen.

fields.name: JSESSIONID
fields.description: New Relic browser monitoring cookie for session tracking and performance analytics (deprecated in newer versions).

fields.name: NREUM
fields.description: New Relic browser monitoring cookie for real user monitoring and performance tracking.
